<link type='text/css' href='css/modal.css' rel='stylesheet' media='screen' />

<script src="//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script type='text/javascript' src='js/jquery.simplemodal-1.4.4.js'></script>

<h2>Sign Up</h2>

<p>
First, you'll need to create (free) accounts for the two services that power CityVoice: Twilio and Heroku.
</p>

<div id="twilio-button" class="button-prominent">
Create a Twilio account
</div>

<br><br>

<div id="heroku-button" class="button-prominent">
Create a Heroku account
</div>

<p>
When you're done, click "Next" below to continue.
</p>

<form name="input" action="/deployment/new" method="post">
<input type="submit" value="Next">
</form>

<div id="heroku-modal-content">
<h4>Create a Heroku account</h4>
<ol>
  <li>Click <a href="https://signup.heroku.com/www-home-top" target="_blank" class="button">here</a>to open a new tab with the Heroku sign-up page</li>
  <li>Create a new account with your email address</li>
  <li>Check your email for a confirmation from Heroku, and follow the link there to set your password</li>
</ol>
<p>
When you're done, click anywhere outside this help window to close it.
</p>
</div>

<div id="twilio-modal-content">
<h4>Create a Twilio account</h4>
<ol>
  <li>Click <a href="https://www.twilio.com/try-twilio" target="_blank" class="button">here</a>to open a new tab with the Twilio sign-up page</li>
  <li>Fill out the sign-up form and follow their instructions for verifying your account</li>
  <li>When you see this:
  <img src="/img/twilio-first-phone-number.png" style="border: solid; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
  Click <strong>"Get started"</strong> and come back to this page</li>
</ol>
<p>
When you're done, click anywhere outside this help window to close it.
</p>
</div>

<script>
  jQuery(function ($) {
    // Load dialog on page load
    //$('#basic-modal-content').modal();

    // Load dialog on click
    $('#twilio-button').click(function (e) {
      $('#twilio-modal-content').modal({
        overlayClose: true
      });
      return false;
    });
    $('#heroku-button').click(function (e) {
      $('#heroku-modal-content').modal({
        overlayClose: true
      });
      return false;
    });
  });
</script>

<style>
#twilio-modal-content {display:none;}
</style>
